hamilton beach brands  wikipedia hamilton beach brands from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search hamilton beach brands inc type subsidiary founded april  founder frederick j osius headquarters glen allen virginia us area served north america products home appliances parent nacco industries subsidiaries proctor silex website wwwhamiltonbeachcom hamilton beach brands inc is an american manufacturer of home appliances and commercial restaurant equipment marketed primarily in the united states canada and mexico including blenders mixers toasters slow cookers clothes irons and air purifiers until sometime in the s the companys products were marketed under the brand name hamilton beach scovill reflecting a merger that occurred in the s in  the company merged with proctor silex another household appliance manufacturer key market competitors include cuisinart black  decker salton delonghi and sunbeam contents  history  products  references  external links historyedit founded in april  by inventor frederick j osius in racine wisconsin the hamilton beach manufacturing company took its name from two men osius hired louis hamilton and chester beach he hired hamilton as the new companys advertising manager and beach to work as a mechanic osius did not care for his own name so he paid hamilton and beach  each for the right to use their names instead the company mostly sold products that osius had invented and patented but chester beach had invented a highspeed fractional motor in  which the company used in many of its products osius designed the agitator implement for the companys first drink mixer the cyclone introduced in  hamilton and beach left the company in  to form their own firm wisconsin electric company osius sold hamiltonbeach to scovill manufacturing in  and moved to millionaires row in miami beach the hamilton beach drink mixer with its characteristic spindle and metal container was found at soda fountains of drug stores throughout north america other products included stand mixers for making batter fans and hair dryers the spindle drink mixer was expanded in the s to enable multiple milk shakes to be processed at once the original company continues as the hamilton beach side of hamilton beach brands inc as of  all of hamilton beachs appliances are manufactured by subcontractors in china productsedit blenders coffeemakers deep fryers electric kettles electric knives food processors indoor grills induction cooktops juicers mixers ovens pizza makers popcorn makers slow cookers steamers toasters referencesedit  hamilton beach brands inc hoovers retrieved    celebrating  years vibrator capitol of the world retrieved    hagerty james r  may  once made in china jobs trickle back to us plants wall street journal  external linksedit hamilton beach proctor silex eclectrics allmetal appliances trueair aircare appliances brewstation cupactivated dispensing carafeless coffeemaker hamilton beach in ukraine v t e nacco industries subsidiaries hamilton beach le gourmet chef north american coal corporation proctor silex former subsidiaries hyster company yale materials handling corporation v t e home appliance brands bauknecht bedazzler beko braun breville bsh hausgeräte neff bticino candy colstonariston cuisinart danby de dietrich remeha delonghi dongbu daewoo electronics dustbot dyson edesa electrolux eureka frigidaire lenhel parkinson cowan whitewestinghouse zanussi fukuda fulgor gaggenau hausgeräte gaggia giacomini gorenje gree electric haier hotpoint hamilton beach brands hisense hisense kelon ikea ivle insinkerator irobot roomba scooba kenmore kleenmaid lehel lg electronics lofra magic bullet magic chef magister medion midea group miele morphy richards newell brands crockpot holmes mr coffee sunbeam olympic group oxo pars khazar peerlesspremier appliance company picabot bosch rowenta russell hobbs saeco samsung electronics servis sharp corporation sisil skyworth smeg snowa subzero tiger corporation toastmaster vestel